 "data": "@startuml
title GreenRoute: Professional Tracking & Notification Sequence

skinparam Style strictuml
skinparam SequenceMessageAlignment center

actor Driver
participant \"Driver PWA\n(Frontend)\" as DriverApp
participant \"Auth Service\n(Firebase)\" as Auth
database \"Realtime DB\n(Firebase)\" as DB
participant \"Notification\nService\" as Notif
participant \"Admin Dashboard\n(Management)\" as AdminApp
participant \"Passenger PWA\n(Client)\" as PassengerApp
actor Passenger

== 1. Session & Route Initialization ==

Driver -> DriverApp : Click \"Start Trip\"
DriverApp -> Auth : Validate Session Token 
Auth --> DriverApp : Token Valid (Role: DRIVER)

DriverApp -> DB : Fetch Assigned Route & Stops 
DB --> DriverApp : Route Data Received

DriverApp -> DB : UPDATE /buses/{id} (Status=\"ACTIVE\") 
DB --> AdminApp : Event: Bus Status Changed (ACTIVE) 
DriverApp <-- DB : Write Success
Driver <-- DriverApp : Show \"Tracking Active\" Dashboard

== 2. Continuous Tracking & Notification Loop ==

loop Every 5 Seconds [cite: 44]
 DriverApp -> DriverApp : Get Hardware GPS Signal 
 DriverApp -> DriverApp : Sanitize Data (Null/Zero Check)
 
 DriverApp -> DB : PUT /locations/{bus_id} {lat, lng, timestamp} 
 
 DB -> PassengerApp : Broadcast: onChildChanged(New Coords) 
 DB -> AdminApp : Broadcast: onChildChanged(New Coords) 
 
 group Passenger-Side Processing
 PassengerApp -> PassengerApp : Apply Smoothing/Interpolation Algorithm 
 PassengerApp -> PassengerApp : Recalculate ETA 
 PassengerApp -> PassengerApp : Refresh Map UI (Smooth Marker Move) 
 end
 
 opt Proximity Alert Trigger 
 PassengerApp -> Notif : Trigger sendPushAlert() if Distance < 500m 
 Notif -> Passenger : Display \"Bus Arriving Soon\" Alert 
 end
end

== 3. Trip Termination ==

Driver -> DriverApp : Click \"Stop Trip\" 
DriverApp -> DB : UPDATE /buses/{id} (Status=\"IDLE\") 
DB -> AdminApp : Event: Status Changed (IDLE)
DB -> PassengerApp : Event: Bus Removed from Live Map
DriverApp <-- DB : Write Success
Driver <-- DriverApp : Show Trip Summary
